1
00:00:22,690 --> 00:00:24,710
Uh... what did you just say?

2
00:00:24,711 --> 00:00:26,186
Wait, you know him?

3
00:00:26,187 --> 00:00:28,042
He's the guy your snack hit earlier.

4
00:00:28,042 --> 00:00:29,120
Oh? Uh...

5
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:30,764
Oh, I'm sorry.

6
00:00:30,764 --> 00:00:32,764
How is this possible...

7
00:00:33,567 --> 00:00:35,582
Is he pissed off?

8
00:00:36,050 --> 00:00:37,960
I really am sorry about the snack,

9
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:40,294
so... wanna grab food with us?

10
00:00:42,700 --> 00:00:44,464
Me?

11
00:00:49,809 --> 00:00:53,153
So what department are you in, and what year?

12
00:00:53,823 --> 00:00:58,692
Ah, I'm a freshman in Visual Design.

13
00:00:58,693 --> 00:01:01,395
Oh really? Huh?

14
00:01:01,396 --> 00:01:03,499
Then you're in the same department as him.

15
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:05,312
Ah...?

16
00:01:05,312 --> 00:01:07,312
Wow, what a coincidence.

17
00:01:08,181 --> 00:01:11,190
And seriously, I'm really sorry about before

18
00:01:11,190 --> 00:01:13,420
I threw it at Lee Hyunjun,

19
00:01:13,420 --> 00:01:15,455
I had no idea it'd fly your way.

20
00:01:15,455 --> 00:01:17,023
You were pretty pissed, right?

21
00:01:17,024 --> 00:01:18,913
Your looked pissed...

22
00:01:20,062 --> 00:01:21,527
No, no, no, I'm okay

23
00:01:21,528 --> 00:01:24,129
I was just... a little startled.

24
00:01:24,130 --> 00:01:27,420
Ah, I'm Kim Yunghui, a sophomore in Taekwondo...

25
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:29,130
and this guy, like I said,

26
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:31,884
is Lee Hyunjun, a sophomore in Visual Design.

27
00:01:31,885 --> 00:01:33,919
What's your name, freshman?

28
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:37,044
My name is Kang Jihan.

29
00:01:37,044 --> 00:01:38,880
Kang Jihan?

30
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:41,795
Kang Jihan... Kang Jihan...

31
00:01:41,795 --> 00:01:43,780
Damn, that's a cool name.

32
00:01:48,295 --> 00:01:49,579
Alright, that's enough, you two...

33
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:51,385
I'm leaving by myself.

34
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,344
What did he mean earlier..

35
00:01:57,345 --> 00:01:59,639
Ugh, I'm starving.

36
00:02:11,211 --> 00:02:13,180
Since you're a junior, I'll be casual.

37
00:02:13,180 --> 00:02:15,170
You can just call me hyung too.

38
00:02:15,170 --> 00:02:16,860
But you two seriously don't know each other?

39
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:19,192
You're in the same department.

40
00:02:20,466 --> 00:02:22,189
Uh...

41
00:02:22,189 --> 00:02:24,189
We just... met.

42
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:27,220
You got any upperclassmen you know?

43
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,148
No...

44
00:02:28,148 --> 00:02:30,010
Any close friends?

45
00:02:30,404 --> 00:02:31,950
Not really...

46
00:02:31,958 --> 00:02:35,115
Uh... are you kind of a noob?

47
00:02:36,315 --> 00:02:39,339
I guess I am...

48
00:02:41,501 --> 00:02:44,639
Hey, then I guess you can take good care of him.

49
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:47,330
He may be stiff, but he's a good guy.

50
00:02:47,330 --> 00:02:50,550
It's nice having an upperclassman in your department.

51
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:53,100
Honestly, Lee Hyunjun only had me as a friend, so...

52
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:54,680
it was kind of concerning

53
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:57,384
I mean, he does look a little hard to approach...

54
00:02:57,384 --> 00:02:59,025
Hey.

55
00:02:59,370 --> 00:03:01,370
See? Exactly this.

56
00:03:03,697 --> 00:03:05,886
I'll get going first.

57
00:03:35,109 --> 00:03:37,604
Ah, what do I do...

58
00:03:37,604 --> 00:03:40,654
The smear made all the Chinese characters
look even more alike.

59
00:03:44,010 --> 00:03:45,759
Right!

60
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:48,321
I'll just go back up to the underworld first.

61
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:50,997
They'll sort this out up there.

62
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,871
O great administrator of the heavens...

63
00:03:57,871 --> 00:04:02,989
Summoned by a place higher and darker,
I answer the call...

64
00:04:05,182 --> 00:04:08,061
Ow... ow!

65
00:04:10,695 --> 00:04:11,777
What?

66
00:04:11,778 --> 00:04:13,887
Did I just get rejected?

67
00:04:14,654 --> 00:04:16,623
Ah!

68
00:04:16,923 --> 00:04:19,046
I have to bring the dead soul first?

69
00:04:19,746 --> 00:04:22,415
Then what the hell am I supposed to do?

70
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:25,539
Hey... hey, you there

71
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:27,989
I can't bring anyone yet...

72
00:04:28,781 --> 00:04:30,878
Hey! Hey!

73
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:43,465
Lee Hyunjun! What are you doing?

74
00:04:45,313 --> 00:04:46,854
What's that?

75
00:04:46,855 --> 00:04:48,407
Ah, it's nothing.

76
00:04:48,408 --> 00:04:49,651
Why all of a sudden?

77
00:04:49,652 --> 00:04:52,118
Mm, no reason, just...

78
00:04:52,758 --> 00:04:54,794
But did something happen?

79
00:04:54,794 --> 00:04:55,662
Something?

80
00:04:55,662 --> 00:04:56,600
Yeah.

81
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,338
You don't look so great.

82
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:01,588
I'm just... kinda tired, I guess.

83
00:05:02,042 --> 00:05:02,910
Well,

84
00:05:02,911 --> 00:05:05,231
our class was pretty brutal.

85
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:07,447
Oh.

86
00:05:07,447 --> 00:05:10,897
Do you know any of the freshmen in our department?

87
00:05:10,897 --> 00:05:12,400
Know them how well?

88
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:15,575
I met this freshman named Kang Jihan today.

89
00:05:15,575 --> 00:05:16,440
Kang Jihan?

90
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,958
Yeah, you know him?

91
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:19,980
Not really.

92
00:05:19,981 --> 00:05:21,301
Why all of a sudden?

93
00:05:21,302 --> 00:05:22,555
Well...

94
00:05:22,555 --> 00:05:23,709
we bumped into each other,

95
00:05:23,710 --> 00:05:25,111
and I spilled coffee on him

96
00:05:25,111 --> 00:05:27,427
so everything he was holding got soaked.

97
00:05:27,428 --> 00:05:29,659
But he looked so upset about it.

98
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:30,840
So I thought if you knew him,

99
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:33,200
I'd get him a little gift or something.

100
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:35,000
But nobody seems to know him.

101
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,970
Did that freshman happen to say anything weird to you?

102
00:05:37,970 --> 00:05:39,379
Anything weird?

103
00:05:39,379 --> 00:05:39,950
Never mind

104
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:41,661
I don't really know him either,

105
00:05:41,661 --> 00:05:42,782
so that's too bad.

106
00:05:42,782 --> 00:05:43,870
Yeah.

107
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:45,490
Let me know if you find out later.

108
00:05:45,490 --> 00:05:46,860
Okay, I will.

109
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:49,135
Alright, I'm heading out first.

110
00:06:18,752 --> 00:06:20,239
Ah...

111
00:06:21,072 --> 00:06:23,072
Shit...

112
00:06:25,699 --> 00:06:28,841
Just wait till I get back up there.

113
00:06:30,406 --> 00:06:32,926
I can get back, right?

114
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:35,815
Hey, Lee Hyunjun!

115
00:06:35,815 --> 00:06:37,815
Huh? Oh, what?

116
00:06:37,815 --> 00:06:39,310
It's you Jihan.

117
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:41,341
You're still here?

118
00:06:41,780 --> 00:06:44,340
Uh... yeah.

119
00:06:44,340 --> 00:06:46,413
Just finishing some assignments.

120
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:49,081
Why are you still on campus, hyung?

121
00:06:49,082 --> 00:06:51,820
Ah, I still had some work to do too

122
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:53,413
I was looking for Hyunjun..

123
00:06:53,414 --> 00:06:55,268
Oh.

124
00:06:55,268 --> 00:06:58,304
Come to think of it,
you said you're in Visual Design, right?

125
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:03,883
You want me to draw the club logo?

126
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:05,292
Yeah.

127
00:07:05,292 --> 00:07:08,749
Since you're in Visual Design,
I figured you'd be good at it

128
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:12,105
I asked Hyunjun too, but he shut me down hard.

129
00:07:12,105 --> 00:07:14,105
Ah...

130
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,297
I...

131
00:07:17,297 --> 00:07:20,266
Please, I'm begging you.
You're my only option, okay?

132
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,555
Just this once.

133
00:07:36,353 --> 00:07:40,893
But why did you start something
like a Chinese Character Club...?

134
00:07:41,033 --> 00:07:44,650
Ah, my grandpa was a classical Chinese scholar.

135
00:07:44,650 --> 00:07:48,120
He used to teach me Chinese characters
ever since I was little,

136
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:51,150
so I naturally got attached to them.

137
00:07:51,150 --> 00:07:54,460
But after he passed away,
drifting away from Chinese characters

138
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:57,340
felt like I was slowly forgetting him too.

139
00:07:57,341 --> 00:08:01,434
So when I got to college,
I made this club to study it properly.

140
00:08:19,253 --> 00:08:21,530
Um...

141
00:08:26,337 --> 00:08:28,913
How about something like this?

142
00:08:29,207 --> 00:08:31,804
Oh, that's really good.

143
00:08:32,593 --> 00:08:34,840
You've definitely got some talent.

144
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,730
Mm~.

145
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:45,618
Ah...

146
00:08:54,207 --> 00:08:55,271
[Hyung, this is bad Hyung!!!

147
00:08:55,295 --> 00:08:56,620
Can I not go back to the underworld for a bit?

148
00:08:56,644 --> 00:08:57,878
Text me when you see this!! Please!!!]

149
00:09:32,052 --> 00:09:34,007
Huh? That's...

150
00:09:34,007 --> 00:09:36,910
Wait, is that Jihan?

151
00:09:44,756 --> 00:09:46,472
Wait.

152
00:09:53,507 --> 00:09:56,055
Well, well, well...

153
00:09:58,300 --> 00:10:01,300
"Fix the Error!"
